<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>630</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào zǒu yī tiáo xuān jiào de lù, shì gēn zhe yé sū zǒu. bǎ fú yīn chuán gěi pín qióng rén, ràng shòu yā zhě dé zì yóu.
 bù guǎn yǒu duō jiān nán méi yǒu hòu tuì de lǐ yóu. bù néng zǒu dà lù zǒu xiǎo lù, yī dìng yào zǒu biàn quán qiú.
 wǒ men yào chuán nǎ, hái yǒu yī diǎn diǎn de shí hòu. cì yú wàn yǒu de quán bǐng, jǐn jǐn wò zài shǒu.
 bù yào pà zhǐ yào xìn, zhí dǐ hēi àn de de fāng. shèng guò chóu dí de zhǔ yé sū, zhèng wèi nǐ kāi lù.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men yào zǒu yī tiáo xuān jiào de lù 迦南630</title>
</song>